OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fbecome more widespread through the
OL,7,Fevening, perhaps merging to longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain. It will be a mainly
OL,9,Fcloudy night with further showers
OL,10,Fspreading east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals and showers.
OL,14,FShowers may be heavy and merge to give
OL,15,Flonger spells of rain. Becoming drier
OL,16,Ffrom the west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
